{
  "_comment": "Composed cloud-ml verification chain (owner domain knowledge 2026-06-11) — enable when the SCR auth key is configured.",
  "lifecycles": [
    {
      "id": "gen-cloudml-chain",
      "service": "ai-ml/cloud-ml",
      "enabled": true,
      "_note": "composed cloud-ml full chain — 9-node closure: keypair/registry/k8s-version/sg/vpc/subnet/filestorage -> ske-cluster -> cloud-ml; needs credential scr-auth-key. ENABLED 2026-06-14. The SCR registry credential is injected SECURELY via {env:...} tokens in the create-cloud-ml body (custom_registry_* + product_group_id) -> resolved from runner env vars (GitHub secrets), never committed. requires_env gates the whole lifecycle: if any of SCP_SCR_REGISTRY_HOST / SCP_SCR_ACCESS_KEY / SCP_SCR_ACCESS_SECRET_KEY / SCP_SCR_PROJECT_ID / SCP_CLOUDML_PRODUCT_GROUP_ID is unset, it env-skips instead of firing a doomed request. OWNER must set those 5 GitHub repo secrets (workflow passes them through) before a live run. heavy + billable (~40-60min, own SKE cluster + VPC) — run in a dedicated isolated window (crud_filter=gen-cloudml-chain). Some body fields (cpu/memory/analytics_resource/application_resource) remain UNPROVEN until the first live run.",
      "steps": [
        {
          "name": "create-cloudml-image",
          "service": "cloud-ml",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/cloud-ml/images",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "image_id": "$.images[0].id"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-keypair",
          "service": "virtualserver",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/keypairs",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrkey{unique}",
            "tags": []
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/keypairs/regrkey{unique}",
            "service": "virtualserver"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-container-registry",
          "service": "scr",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/container-registries",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrscr{unique}",
            "private_acl_enabled": false,
            "private_acl_resources": [],
            "public_acl_resources": [],
            "public_visible_enabled": false
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "reg_id": "$.id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/container-registries/{reg_id}",
            "service": "scr"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "wait-container-registry",
          "service": "scr",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/container-registries/{reg_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200
          ],
          "poll": {
            "field": "$.state",
            "until": [
              "Running",
              "RUNNING",
              "active",
              "ACTIVE"
            ],
            "timeout": 180,
            "interval": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-kubernetes-version",
          "service": "ske",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/kubernetes-versions",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "kube_ver": "$.kubernetes_versions[0].kubernetes_version"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-security-group",
          "service": "security-group",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/security-groups",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrsg{unique}",
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "loggable": false,
            "tags": []
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "sg_id": "$.security_group.id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/security-groups/{sg_id}",
            "service": "security-group"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-vpc",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/vpcs",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrvpc{unique}",
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "cidr": "10.160.0.0/20",
            "tags": []
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "vpc_id": "$.vpc.id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/vpcs/{vpc_id}",
            "service": "vpc"
          },
          "adopt": "vpc"
        },
        {
          "name": "wait-vpc",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/vpcs/{vpc_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200
          ],
          "poll": {
            "field": "$.vpc.state",
            "until": [
              "ACTIVE"
            ],
            "timeout": 180,
            "interval": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-subnet",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/subnets",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrsub{unique}",
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "cidr": "10.160.8.0/24",
            "type": "GENERAL",
            "vpc_id": "{vpc_id}",
            "tags": []
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "subnet_id": "$.subnet.id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/subnets/{subnet_id}",
            "service": "vpc"
          },
          "adopt": "subnet"
        },
        {
          "name": "wait-subnet",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/subnets/{subnet_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200
          ],
          "poll": {
            "field": "$.subnet.state",
            "until": [
              "ACTIVE"
            ],
            "timeout": 180,
            "interval": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-filestorage-volume",
          "service": "filestorage",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/volumes",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrfs{unique}",
            "protocol": "NFS",
            "type_name": "HDD"
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "volume_id": "$.volume_id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/volumes/{volume_id}",
            "service": "filestorage"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "wait-filestorage-volume",
          "service": "filestorage",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/volumes/{volume_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200
          ],
          "poll": {
            "field": "$.state",
            "until": [
              "available",
              "AVAILABLE",
              "ACTIVE"
            ],
            "timeout": 300,
            "interval": 15
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-ske-cluster",
          "service": "ske",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/clusters",
          "json": {
            "name": "regrske{unique}",
            "kubernetes_version": "{kube_ver}",
            "cloud_logging_enabled": "false",
            "vpc_id": "{vpc_id}",
            "subnet_id": "{subnet_id}",
            "security_group_id_list": [
              "{sg_id}"
            ],
            "private_endpoint_access_control_resources": [],
            "tags": [],
            "volume_id": "{volume_id}",
            "public_endpoint_access_control_ip": "0.0.0.0/0",
            "service_watch_logging_enabled": "true"
          },
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "cluster_id": "$.resource_id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/clusters/{cluster_id}",
            "service": "ske"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "wait-ske-cluster",
          "service": "ske",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/clusters/{cluster_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200
          ],
          "poll": {
            "field": "$.cluster.status",
            "until": [
              "RUNNING",
              "ACTIVE",
              "Running"
            ],
            "timeout": 1800,
            "interval": 30
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "create-cloud-ml",
          "service": "cloud-ml",
          "method": "POST",
          "path": "/v1/cloud-ml",
          "json": {
            "cloud_ml_name": "regr-cloudml-{ualpha}",
            "description": "API regression suite",
            "cluster_id": "{cluster_id}",
            "image_id": "{image_id}",
            "product_group_id": "{env:SCP_CLOUDML_PRODUCT_GROUP_ID}",
            "domain_name": "regr-cloudml-{ualpha}",
            "endpoint_type": "PUBLIC",
            "custom_registry_host": "{env:SCP_SCR_REGISTRY_HOST}",
            "custom_registry_access_key": "{env:SCP_SCR_ACCESS_KEY}",
            "custom_registry_access_secret_key": "{env:SCP_SCR_ACCESS_SECRET_KEY}",
            "custom_registry_access_project_id": "{env:SCP_SCR_PROJECT_ID}",
            "custom_registry_access_region": "{region}",
            "use_copilot": false,
            "analytics_resource": {
              "cpu": 1,
              "gpu": "",
              "memory": 2
            },
            "application_resource": {
              "cpu": 1,
              "memory": 2
            },
            "copilot": {
              "cpu": 0,
              "gpu": "",
              "memory": 0
            },
            "tags": []
          },
          "_note": "product_group_id + custom_registry_* are owner-fill literals — engine has NO env->body substitution (regression/scenarios/engine.py _fill/_fill_obj resolve only builtins + prior captures), and create-container-registry captures only reg_id, so the console-issued SCR auth key cannot be wired automatically. custom_registry_host/access_key/access_secret_key are documented required (data/validation_findings.json:169-181); product_group_id + custom_registry_access_project_id/access_region appear in data/api_bodies.json createcloudml but are UNPROVEN-required (no doc constraint). custom_registry_access_region defaulted to {region}; remove any field the live API rejects as unknown. This key is a step-level sibling of json (NOT in the body) so the engine never sends it.",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            201,
            202
          ],
          "capture": {
            "cloud_ml_id": "$.id"
          },
          "cleanup": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "path": "/v1/cloud-ml/{cloud_ml_id}",
            "service": "cloud-ml"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verify-cloud-ml",
          "service": "cloud-ml",
          "method": "GET",
          "path": "/v1/cloud-ml/{cloud_ml_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-cloud-ml",
          "service": "cloud-ml",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/cloud-ml/{cloud_ml_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204
          ],
          "destructive": true
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-ske-cluster",
          "service": "ske",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/clusters/{cluster_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-filestorage-volume",
          "service": "filestorage",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/volumes/{volume_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-subnet",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/subnets/{subnet_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30,
          "adopt": "subnet"
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-vpc",
          "service": "vpc",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/vpcs/{vpc_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30,
          "adopt": "vpc"
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-security-group",
          "service": "security-group",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/security-groups/{sg_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-container-registry",
          "service": "scr",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/container-registries/{reg_id}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30
        },
        {
          "name": "delete-keypair",
          "service": "virtualserver",
          "method": "DELETE",
          "path": "/v1/keypairs/regrkey{unique}",
          "expect_status": [
            200,
            202,
            204,
            409,
            404
          ],
          "destructive": true,
          "retry_on_status": [
            409
          ],
          "retries": 40,
          "retry_interval": 30
        }
      ],
      "credentials": [
        "scr-auth-key"
      ],
      "heavy": true,
      "_disabled_reason": "READY but gated: (1) SCR 인증키(scr-auth-key)가 테스트 계정에 미설정 — 소유자 콘솔 발급 대기, 없으면 cloud-ml create가 registry-credential 단계에서 실패(소유자 지식); (2) heavy chain — ske-cluster 포함 ~40-60분+과금. 인증키 설정 후 heavy=true scoped run으로 검증",
      "requires_env": [
        "SCP_SCR_REGISTRY_HOST",
        "SCP_SCR_ACCESS_KEY",
        "SCP_SCR_ACCESS_SECRET_KEY",
        "SCP_SCR_PROJECT_ID",
        "SCP_CLOUDML_PRODUCT_GROUP_ID"
      ]
    }
  ]
}